        <mxCell id="nEbZi96V4aJNZWkyk8Nh-19" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Use&lt;div&gt;TENEBRION_STATE&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;on&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;/data/Tenebrion/tenebrion.txt&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;To determine the state. If the state is same then it will not execute the script. Script is only executed only if the state changed (Prevent Loop Script Execution)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
