        <mxCell id="b3YdXMALDGP9B1bVFv12-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="Pretty Much Language Handling List&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Main core = C&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Detect Screen State = Assembly&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Write to sysfs = Assembly&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;USING SHELL IS PROHIBITED&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(&lt;b&gt;Probably&lt;/b&gt;, If for monitoring the file using Assembly is bloated will use inotify API, but I doubt inotify will be better than my Assembly)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;TODO: Patch the build.sh since project structure is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Modules/&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Binaries/&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Sources/&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;build.sh&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Running build.sh will put the compiled binary to Modules/Binaries&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
